<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f4f4f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f766e, #22c55e);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #0f172a;
    }
    .message {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #475569;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 40px 0;
    }
    .verify-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f766e, #22c55e);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .verify-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .alternative-link {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .alternative-link p {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #64748b;
    }
    .alternative-link a {
      color: #0f766e;
      word-break: break-all;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .info-box {
      background: #f0fdf4;
      border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .info-box p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #166534;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #64748b;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #0f766e;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Welcome to Sign in with Face</h1>
      <p>Just one more step to complete your signup</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="greeting">
        Hi <%= @full_name %>,
      </div>
      
      <div class="message">
        <p>Thank you for registering with <b>Sign in with Face</b>. Weâ€™re pleased to welcome you aboard.</p>
        <p>To complete your account setup and enable Sign in with Face, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="button-container">
        <%= link_to 'Verify Email Address', @verification_url, class: 'verify-button' %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <p>For your security, this verification link will expire in 1 hour.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="alternative-link">
        <p>If you are unable to use the button above, you may copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
        <%= link_to @verification_url, @verification_url %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="message" style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <p><strong>What to Expect Next</strong></p>
        <ol style="padding-left: 20px; margin: 10px 0;">
          <li>Click the verification link.</li>
          <li>Scan the QR code using your Axiam's Sign in with Face Authenticator app (Download here <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.docerfy.axiam_v2" style="color: #0f766e; text-decoration: none;">Android</a>, <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/axiam/id6499258374" style="color: #0f766e; text-decoration: none;">iOS</a> app).</li>
          <li>Complete the facial scan on your mobile device.</li>
          <li>Begin signing in quickly and securely with facial recognition.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact us at <%= mail_to 'support@axiam.io', 'support@axiam.io', style: 'color: #0f766e; text-decoration: none;' %>.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 20px;">Thank you for joining us!</p>
      <p>â€” The Sign in with Face Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
